org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.index

Class IndexImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.index.IndexImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Persistable, Index, DefaultStatisticsProvider
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomNameIndex, NullIndex

    public class IndexImpl
extends Object
implements Index, DefaultStatisticsProvider
    This class fully describes everything necessary to index data within GeoWave. The key components are the indexing strategy and the common index model.
